messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning-intent 项目的 attribute agent。
只归因当前单轮 intent-recognition 链路：request_normalization、intent_api_call、adapter_extraction、label_mapping；不要把 planning/SSE generation 的问题归入本项目。
优先使用 intent_contract_probe 定位 intent label、required slots/entities、confidence threshold、fallback policy 或 label_mapping 的当前证据差异。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图标签为customer_portrait",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_api_call",
          "file": "app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py",
          "element": "intent classification prompt",
          "reason": "模型未输出 customer_portrait 意图，可能提示词缺少该类意图的定义或样本"
        },
        {
          "stage": "adapter_extraction",
          "file": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py",
          "element": "intent extraction logic",
          "reason": "从原始响应中提取意图标签时未能解析为 customer_portrait，可能默认回退为 other"
        },
        {
          "stage": "label_mapping",
          "file": "app/schemas/intent.py",
          "element": "INTENT_MAPPING",
          "reason": "raw_intent=None 或未知标签被映射为 other，未将对应模式纠正为 customer_portrait"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "上游识别与提取环节未能产出 customer_portrait 标签，而 label_mapping 保持 other，导致最终意图错误",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output",
          "detail": "intent: 'other', confidence: 0.5"
        },
        {
          "source": "runtime_checks",
          "detail": "raw_intent=None 经映射变为 other，期望 customer_portrait"
        },
        {
          "source": "intent_contract_probe",
          "detail": "intent_match=false"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "槽位target_value提取为重疾险",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "adapter_extraction",
          "file": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py",
          "element": "slot extraction logic",
          "reason": "未从用户查询或模型响应中提取 target_value 字段，缺少实体识别步骤"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "提取逻辑未实现或未执行槽位提取，或因意图错误导致跳过 target_value 提取",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output",
          "detail": "缺失 target_value 字段"
        },
        {
          "source": "reference_contract",
          "detail": "期望 target_value='重疾险'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "置信度不低于0.95",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_api_call",
          "file": "app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py",
          "element": "confidence scoring",
          "reason": "模型返回置信度仅 0.5，说明分类结果高度不确定"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "模型对查询的分类置信度过低，无法满足 0.95 阈值，根源与意图错误分类一致",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output",
          "detail": "confidence: 0.5"
        },
        {
          "source": "reference_contract",
          "detail": "期望 confidence ≥ 0.95"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "不触发fallback兜底意图",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "label_mapping",
          "file": "app/schemas/intent.py",
          "element": "INTENT_MAPPING",
          "reason": "最终 intent 为 other，即兜底意图，未能避免 fallback"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "整个意图识别流程未正确匹配，导致标签映射落入兜底分支 other",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output",
          "detail": "intent: 'other'"
        },
        {
          "source": "intent_contract_probe",
          "detail": "fallback_observed=false 但实际进入 other 即为兜底"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "客户画像分析调度边界正确",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "因意图标签错误为 other，导致调度无法指向客户画像分析模块，属于意图识别失败的间接结果",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output",
          "detail": "intent: 'other'，导致 dispatch_target='fallback'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "intent_contract",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "all",
          "file": "intent_recognition chain",
          "reason": "整体未满足 reference contract"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "单轮意图识别整体失败，未输出 contract 指定的 intent 与槽位，属于前述根本原因的汇总",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "judge_result",
          "detail": "incorrect，失败项=['intent']"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {
      "stage": "intent_api_call",
      "file": "app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py",
      "element": "prompt definition",
      "reason": "提示词未能引导模型准确分类为客户画像意图，并可能缺失槽位提取指令"
    },
    {
      "stage": "adapter_extraction",
      "file": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py",
      "element": "response parsing & extraction",
      "reason": "解析逻辑未正确提取意图标签及 target_value，并可能设置了默认值 other"
    },
    {
      "stage": "label_mapping",
      "file": "app/schemas/intent.py",
      "element": "INTENT_MAPPING mapping table",
      "reason": "映射表将 raw_intent=None 映射为 other，缺少与 customer_portrait 的映射规则，未能纠正上游错误"
    }
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模型未能将用户查询'帮我看看上季度买了重疾险的客户都是啥样的？'分类为 customer_portrait，adapter_extraction 输出低置信度 other 且未提取 target_value 槽位；label_mapping 将空或未知标签映射为 other，未启用任何纠正机制，导致最终意图与所有期望不符。根本原因在于模型提示词/分类能力不足或 adapter 解析逻辑缺陷，以及映射表缺乏兜底规则来覆盖此类明显属于客户画像的查询。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "type": "extracted_output",
      "data": {
        "intent": "other",
        "confidence": 0.5,
        "subIntent": "其他意图"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "runtime_checks",
      "check": "intent_mapping",
      "result": {
        "raw_intent": null,
        "actual_mapping": "other",
        "expected_intent": "customer_portrait",
        "available_mapping_count": 7,
        "mapping_source": "app/schemas/intent.py:INTENT_MAPPING"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "intent_contract_probe",
      "result": {
        "intent_match": false,
        "actual_confidence": 0.5,
        "evidence_gap": [
          "intent_evidence"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "reference_contract",
      "value": {
        "intent": "customer_portrait",
        "target_value": "重疾险",
        "confidence": 0.95
      }
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "high"
}

